<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE FEATURES BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These feature stories for release Wednesday, Dec. 16, 1998, are
moving today to clients of the New York Times News Service.
</P>
