Netanyahu of Israel before wrapping up his Middle East peace
mission and heading home to face an impeachment vote in the House.
By NANCY MATHIS.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-PALESTINIANS (Bethlehem) _ Songs of joy intertwined with
signs of independence greet President Clinton and his family as
Yasser Arafat and his wife lead them on a tour of Christian sites.
Thousands of Palestinians gather amid neon mangers and plastic
Santas to cheer Clinton's words of support. By DEBORAH HORAN.
