possibility of heading off a Senate trial through parliamentary
maneuvers or a bipartisan censure vote. By Michael Kranish. 1200
words.
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-CLINTON (Washington) _ President Clinton was returning
to ever-dimming prospects that he will avoid impeachment by the
full House. By Ann Scales. 1200 words.
