<P>
   The lede story will move by  &UR; 9:30 p.m. Eastern time &LR; :
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH (Washington) _ Lede-all on impeachment developments:
Clinton returns from the Middle East to find the House apparently
moving inexorably toward impeaching him. All the representatives
who had been declaring themselves to be undecided seem to be
deciding against the president. By Alison Mitchell. (1800 words)
</P>
