   &UR; Lead story: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH (Washington) _ Lede-all on impeachment developments:
leadership meetings, vote decisions by various members, etc. By
Alison Mitchell.
</P>
<P>
   (We plan to move this story by 9 p.m. ET in `w' news file.)
</P>
