<SLUG> BC-LOCKERBIE-LIBYA-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TRIAL OF LOCKERBIE SUSPECTS A STEP CLOSER 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (i and a coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By DAVID L. MARCUS  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Days before the 10th anniversary of the bombing of
